# Data Directory

This directory stores persistent data for the bot.

## Required Files

### twikit_cookies.json
Twitter cookies for authentication. **Do not commit this file to git!**

To get cookies:
1. Log into https://x.com in your browser
2. Install "Get cookies.txt LOCALLY" browser extension
3. Click the extension and download cookies
4. Save as `data/twikit_cookies.json`

Format:
```json
[
  {"name": "auth_token", "value": "...", "domain": ".twitter.com"},
  {"name": "ct0", "value": "...", "domain": ".twitter.com"}
]
```

## Generated Files

- `last_tweet_id.txt` - Last processed tweet ID (auto-created)
- `sentiment.db` - Sentiment analysis database (auto-created)
